summary: CAUTION this will overwrite the texture files for the Slick Catsuit CBBE compatible by Nalim. This is a chainmail texture for his mod and includes the needed files.
descriptionHtml:
CAUTION this will overwrite the texture files for the Slick Catsuit CBBE compatible by Nalim
Nalim created a great catsuit so I just had to make a texture to do it justice, so with his approval, here it is. As mentioned it will overwrite the texture of his original armor with the see-through chainmail. Any use of the armor requires his ok. 

You must install the Main_with_physics_and_slider-12013-1-9.rar by Nalim then install this file, it will overwrite the existing textures and give you a chainmail texture
You can find the original file here
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12013
author: Great Bizarro
